Solid's technology-based app allows people to create their own personal online data store, POD.
It may include lists, to-do lists, calendars, music libraries, and other personal or work tools.
It's as if Google Drive, Microsoft Outlook, Slack and Spotify are available in one browser at the same time.
The online store of personal data is unique in that only the user decides who and which information they can access.
